title: Elven Legacy [PC game] strategy
description:
Elven Legacy.
Game type:- Strategy adventure. 
Game for PC. 
labelled Paradox Interactive.

Requirements [minimum]:-
Vista/XP,
Intel Pentium 1.5GHz,
512 RAM,
3GB free hard drive space.


Copied DVD-ROM [exe].
Delivered in rar folder contains:-
Elven Legacy.exe
Patch, released 4th May 2009.
Short avi video.


Extract the files from the rar folder and run setup, finally install the patch to update the game.

If you havent got a rar extractor installed, download one from the link below, recommend to use 7Zip, once installed simply right click on the downloaded rar folder > 7Zip > extract here.
 <a href="
http://www.filehippo.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.filehippo.com/</a>

The patch for Elven Legacy, addressing a few tutorial issues and the ammount of video memory detected under Windows Vista. Developed by 1C:Ino-Co studio, Elven Legacy features a nonlinear storyline, two primary campaigns, a wide variety of bonus missions, as well as a map editor.
